column5: When are the cats gonna be running again??? Early April, or mid April...I hope to hook into some of them again this year!
This instantly made me think of that Fish n Canada episode.
the ice is out now small ones are up but bigger guys should be coming up soon!
wow, that's a big cat, i'd love to catch some of those, all we have are little weeee "barbottes"
im going to try it out this weekend at fishmasters. i cant take cabin fever anymore, just getting a line in the water will be good.
I'm heading down on tuesday to give it a shot. I know it may be a bit early, but I just can't wait any longer.   meow!
I fish that spot too! Nice kitty
